story.storyDescription: Natasha's just trying not to get caught. But Alex has other plans.
story.title: Sneaking In

messages.text: Heads up, I’m climbing through the basement window.
she thinks ur sleeping, give it a second.
I feel like ur fucking with me on purpose.
it’s midnight, why is she cleaning?
by the way there’s an Iron & Wine concert tomorrow night
and I’m missing it because of ur birthday.
I’m honestly pissed about it. Iron & Wine has seen me through harder times than you’ll ever know.
I’m helping you sneak into our home and all I get is fine?
need updates on moms movements not your concert-missing sadness.
what happens if she sees u?
I’m fine, Dylans fine, we’re all fine in ur world.
mom told me tonight that ur going crazy and becoming a radical thinker.
starting to think she may be right.
so what’s the game plan, wise one?
go to the window in dads office, right by the pool.
try it, she won’t hear you
u have to give it 2 tugs
when u hear the clicking noise, it’s open
u know too much about this
something u want to tell me?
I was a more impressive 16 yr old than you’ll ever be
shit the lights on in here, r u sure I’m good?
fuck, I’m stuck on the edge of the window pane
why under the desk? The door is closed…
but I think you’re good to come out.
she might not see u if ur on ur hands and knees.
BRB, on my hands and knees.
I need your speed to decelerate
wait, I don’t even see mom in the living room.
Iron & Wine, Natasha. Iron & fucking Wine.
